    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 45-35-7, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE PERMANENTLY DISABLED PERSONS WHO ARE RESIDENTS OF NURSING HOMES OR ASSISTED LIVING FACILITIES TO RECEIVE A PERMANENT STATE IDENTIFICATION CARD WITHOUT CHARGE OF A FEE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
